    "statement": "FSRS springs from [MaiMemo's DHP model](https://www.maimemo.com/paper/) ([中文介绍](https://memodocs.maimemo.com/docs/2022_KDD)), which is a variant of the [DSR model](https://supermemo.guru/wiki/Three_component_model_of_memory) proposed by [Piotr Wozniak](https://supermemo.guru/wiki/Piotr_Wozniak).",
